ChatGPT was used selectively during the preparation of this thesis in an assistive role. It supported language refinement, structural review, consistency checks, and the organization of notes and feedback material.

All AI-generated suggestions for the technical descriptions, the interpretation of feedback, and the correct use of sources were reviewed, selected, and revised. AI tools were not used as independent sources of factual claims; factual statements are based on cited literature, project documentation, implementation work, and feedback material.
